  "url": "https://www.ada.lk/breaking_news/\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0dd2\u0dbb-\u0db4\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dca-\u0db1\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd0\u0db6\u0dd6-\u0d8b\u0db4\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dd2\u0db0\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db1\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dda-\u0d9c\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dbd\u0dd4\u0dc0-\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0db3\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf/11-396698",
  "time_ut": 1661756465,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0dd2\u0dbb \u0db4\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dca \u0db1\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd0\u0db6\u0dd6 \u0d8b\u0db4\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dd2\u0db0\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db1\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dda \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dbd\u0dd4\u0dc0 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0db3\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Solving the problem of graduates who did not get permanent appointments",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Prime Minister Dinesh Gunawardena, as the Minister of Public Administration, Home Affairs, Provincial Councils and Local Government, stated in the Parliament that he will work to provide a solution to the problem of the people who did not get appointments due to various problems while giving appointments to the graduates.",
        "Answering a question asked by the opposition leader that 461 people have not received appointments due to various deficiencies, the Prime Minister said that the Ministry Secretary has already started discussions in this regard.",
        "\"Mr. Deputy Speaker, the leader of the opposition mentioned the number of qualified persons who have not yet obtained tenure in the departments under the Ministry of Public Administration. The Ministry Secretary has already started discussions on this issue. I hope to work to find a solution to it.\""
      ],
